<title>GREECE: TELESIS PLACES BLOCK OF AVAX SHARES WITH FUNDS.</title>
<headline>TELESIS PLACES BLOCK OF AVAX SHARES WITH FUNDS.</headline>
<dateline>ATHENS 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Athens bourse member Telesis Securities placed a block of 300,000 shares of construction firm Avax with domestic and foreign institutional investors at 1,940 drachmas a share.</p>
<p>Telesis officials told Reuters the placement will help Avax's 2.06 billion drachma rights issue which was cleared by the stock exchabge authorities on Thursday.</p>
<p>Avax will issue 1.72 million common registered shares at 1,200 drachmas. The terms will be four new shares per 10 outstanding.</p>
<p>It closed at 2,125 drachmas on Friday -- up 54. --George Georgiopoulos, Athens Newsroom +301 3311812-4</p>
